author: vines
msg: Accumulo-41 - 4 spaces beat two spaces, 160 line wrap beat no line wrap. These can be opened for discussion later, but for now that is the standard. The eclipse formatter XML file is located in contrib, so no one can use the excuse that they don't have access to it or that it's not documented.

For note- Do not autoformat the master without fixing the little state diagram for transitionOK[][]. Also, no thrift code is reformated since it's autogenerated. No non-.java class files have been modified because the formatter does not have the same type of behavior for those files as far as I could tell.
